      "content": "i hear you, but i've heard from other people that a tiny bit of alcohol is actually used by some doctors to help people relax when they're on meds. surely there's a middle ground where it's not \"life-threatening\"? like, if i just take a half dose of the diazepam and have my wine, wouldn't that balance out so it's just a light sleep aid? i just really need to stop being so restless.",
